    <item>
      <title>安联经济学家苏布兰谈美联储、欧洲央行降息和油价影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-11/a-10-rise-in-oil-would-raise-european-inflation-by-1-2-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[安联首席经济学家 Ludovic Subran 预计欧洲央行今年将降息 50 个基点 - 然而，石油价格上涨可能会使央行的情况变得复杂，并削弱对美联储降息的预期。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-11/a-10-rise-in-oil-would-raise-european-inflation-by-1-2-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 10:09:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本警告日元贬值，日元交易者对干预持谨慎态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/japan-s-top-currency-official-mulls-all-forex-options-as-needed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本警告称，在日元兑美元汇率跌至1990年以来的最低水平后，日本将考虑采取一切措施来应对日元疲软。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/japan-s-top-currency-official-mulls-all-forex-options-as-needed</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 23:37:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗袭击以色列的风险成为焦点，油价波动至90美元附近</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-11</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员继续关注伊朗或其代理人对以色列的潜在袭击，在连续几天的波动中，油价冷却了前一天的涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-11</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 23:30:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国期货、债券因降息希望减弱而下滑：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国股指期货和债券小幅走低，预示着华尔街将进一步下跌，因为顽固的通胀迫使投资者降低对美联储降息的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 22:45:34 GMT</pubDate>
